<div class='mailer__content'>
  <p class="govuk-body">Dear <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>
  <p class="govuk-body"><strong>Congratulations on achieving your certificate!</strong></p>
  <p class="govuk-body">We are delighted to confirm that your community activities have been verified and you have achieved the national NCCE certificate to Teach secondary computing.</p>
  <p class="govuk-body">
    <%= link_to 'Download your certificate', certificate_secondary_certificate_url, class: 'govuk-button button' %>
  </p>
  <p class="govuk-body">Share your achievement with friends and colleagues by adding your new digital badge to your social media and email.</p>
  <p class="govuk-body">Congratulations on your achievement and please contact <%= mail_to 'info@teachcomputing.org', 'info@teachcomputing', class: 'ncce-link' %> if you have any questions.</p>
